project_descr: The Samoa One UN YEP project is responding to the request from the Government of Samoa to assist in addressing youth unemployment. Its main objective is to assist youth to develop knowledge and skills needed to enter the formal labour market.

outputs.output_descr: The One-UN Samoa Youth Employment Programme (1UN-YEP) is responding to the request from the Government of Samoa to assist in its ongoing efforts to address youth unemployment.
donor_name: UNITED NATIONS EDUCATIONAL, SCIENTIFIC & CULTURAL ORGANIZAITON
